675
00:38:19,091 --> 00:38:20,836
Bagaimana situasinya?

676
00:38:22,161 --> 00:38:24,035
Pekerjaan merebut pacarku.

677
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:28,971
Ini situasi serius.

678
00:38:28,971 --> 00:38:30,175
