844
00:49:58,361 --> 00:49:59,436
Ini dia.

845
00:50:11,801 --> 00:50:12,841
Enak.

846
00:50:12,841 --> 00:50:15,015
Mau kubungkuskan? Aku punya banyak di studio.

847
00:50:16,540 --> 00:50:18,681
